description: The significant size of the Physician Fee Schedule Payment Amount File-National requires that database programs (e.g., Access, dBase, FoxPro, etc.) be used to read these data. Word processing and spreadsheet programs cannot be used. The database programs noted above will also be required to read some versions of the Physician Fee Schedule Payment Amount File Carrier-Specific.
keyword: Publically Available Data File - for download
title: Physician Fee Schedule National Payment Amount File
